    <h2>About Mattel</h2>
    <p>Mattel, Inc., founded in 1945, is a global leader in toy manufacturing. Besides Hot Wheels, Mattel owns famous brands such as Barbie, Fisher-Price, and American Girl. The company is known for creating engaging and imaginative products that inspire kids worldwide.</p>
